  static const String theoryText_2_2 =
      '''Bonds are debt instruments issued by governments or private companies to raise capital. Investors, by purchasing bonds, become creditors and receive interest payments over a specified period. Bonds are generally considered more stable and reliable investments compared to stocks, although their returns may be lower.\n
