  static const String theoryText_4_3 =
      '''The fourth rule of portfolio diversification is to regularly rebalance investments. Market conditions and asset performance can change over time, so investors should periodically review their portfolios and make necessary adjustments. Rebalancing allows investors to maintain an optimal balance between risk and return.\n
