  static const String theoryText_5_4 =
      '''In conclusion, analyzing the financial indicators of companies before investing is a crucial step in the investment decision-making process. Evaluating profitability, liquidity, financial structure, asset utilization efficiency, and market position helps investors determine the value and potential profitability of the company, as well as assess the level of risk associated with the investment. Analyzing financial indicators enables investors to make informed decisions and achieve their investment goals.''';
  static const String theoryText_6_1 =
      '''Technical analysis in investments is one of the primary approaches to decision-making in financial markets. It is based on the examination of price and volume charts, along with the use of various technical indicators to forecast future price movements.\n
