  static const String theoryText_8_2 =
      '''One of the most common emotions associated with investing is fear. Investors may fear losing money or taking risky decisions, leading them to make conservative choices and miss out on profit opportunities. For instance, they might avoid investing in new and promising companies due to fear of the unknown.\n
