  static const String theoryText_8_3 =
      '''Moreover, emotions can affect decisions regarding the timing of investments. Investors might fear missing out on high returns and make impulsive decisions without proper analysis. Conversely, they may delay investments due to fear of losing money. Both approaches can be flawed and lead to missed income opportunities.\n
