  static const String theoryText_10_2 =
      '''The second rule is the development of a trading strategy. Successful traders have a clear and well-thought-out strategy based on market analysis and the prediction of market movements. They identify entry and exit points for trades and set profit targets. They may also utilize various technical indicators and oscillators to make informed decisions.\n
