  static const String theoryText_10_3 =
      '''One trading strategy on the stock market is trend trading. This strategy assumes that stock prices tend to move in one direction over a specific period. Traders identify market trends and open positions in the direction of these trends. They may use various indicators, such as moving averages, to determine the trend's direction.\n
