  static const String theoryText_12_1 =
      '''In recent years, cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology have become the focus of widespread attention. Cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, and Ripple represent digital assets built on blockchain technology. Blockchain is a distributed database that stores transaction information, providing security and transparency.\n
