      '''The development of a startup requires not only financial investment but also intensified efforts in promoting the product or service in the market. Investors can assist in this process by providing not only financial support but also their experience and knowledge. They can actively participate in strategic planning, conduct marketing research, and assist in finding clients and partners.\n
