  static const String theoryText_14_2 =
      '''Another method of real estate investment is through leasing. An investor can acquire property and lease it, generating regular income from rental payments. Leasing can be an attractive strategy for investors who prefer not to engage in property management or lack the capital for outright property purchases.\n
