  static const String theoryText_18_1 =
      '''Investing in funds and Exchange-Traded Funds (ETFs) is one of the most popular methods of capital investment in today's financial markets. These instruments provide investors with the opportunity to diversify their portfolios, reduce risks, and generate stable income.\n
